{"type":null,"faqId":34038,"title":" Why can't my phone be discovered by other Bluetooth devices?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:end;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>Bluetooth has been turned off on your phone. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Solution 1: Go to </span><span class=\"s2\">Settings</span><span> and turn on Bluetooth.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109353\" style=\"width:1.9694444in;height:3.3652778in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109354\" style=\"width:1.9923611in;height:3.3493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109355\" style=\"width:1.9256945in;height:3.3534722in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>Solution 2: Turn on Bluetooth from the notification panel.</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109356\" style=\"width:1.9680556in;height:3.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109357\" style=\"width:1.9680556in;height:3.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p  >\n <span>Bluetooth is turned on, but your phone is not set to be visible to other devices.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Solution: Go to </span><span class=\"s2\">Settings</span><span> and touch </span><span class=\"s2\">Bluetooth</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Visibility</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109358\" style=\"width:1.7402778in;height:3.0951388in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p  >\n <span>The Bluetooth detection has timed out.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Solution 1: Touch </span><span class=\"s2\">Settings</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Bluetooth</span><span>, turn off </span><span class=\"s2\">Visibility</span><span> and turn it back on to recount the detection time. (Refer to the preceding figure.)</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"_Toc413916401\"><span>Touch </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109359\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Visibility timeout</span><span> and set a longer timeout period.</span></a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"8738","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436779650000,"seriesProductName":"CHC-U01","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"CHC-U01,G play mini","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}